My-Guide

Step 1: Scroll down to footer.

Step 2: Click "Builder" link

This will open the builder.

Step 3: Click "Create New Form" button

Step 4: Type "My Form" in "Form Name"

Step 5: Click "Create Form" button in dialog

Step 6: Click "Add Field" button

Step 7: Click "Text" button

Step 8: Click element

Step 9: Click "Write here..." field

Step 10: Type "Enter something here." in "Write here..."

Step 11: Click "Validation" button

Step 12: Click "+ Add Rule" button

Step 13: Click element

Step 14: Select "required"

Step 15: Click element

Step 16: Type "This field is required." in "Message (optional)"

Step 17: Click "Save" button in navigation

Step 18: Click "Open" in navigation

Step 19: Type "Hello" in "Field 0"
